fields.name: AgentConfiguration
fields.description: The machine configuration of the run agent.

fields.name: AgentPoolName
fields.description: The dedicated agent pool for the run.

fields.name: CreateTime
fields.description: The time the run was scheduled.

fields.name: CustomRegistries
fields.description: The list of custom registries that were logged in during this run.

fields.name: FinishTime
fields.description: The time the run finished.

fields.name: ImageUpdateTrigger
fields.description: The image update trigger that caused the run. This is applicable if the task has base image trigger configured.

fields.name: IsArchiveEnabled
fields.description: The value that indicates whether archiving is enabled or not.

fields.name: LastUpdatedTime
fields.description: The last updated time for the run.

fields.name: LogArtifact
fields.description: The image description for the log artifact.

fields.name: OutputImages
fields.description: The list of all images that were generated from the run. This is applicable if the run generates base image dependencies.

fields.name: Platform
fields.description: The platform properties against which the run will happen.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of a run.

fields.name: RunErrorMessage
fields.description: The error message received from backend systems after the run is scheduled.

fields.name: RunId
fields.description: The unique identifier for the run.

fields.name: RunType
fields.description: The type of run.

fields.name: SourceRegistryAuth
fields.description: The scope of the credentials that were used to login to the source registry during this run.

fields.name: SourceTrigger
fields.description: The source trigger that caused the run.

fields.name: StartTime
fields.description: The time the run started.

fields.name: Status
fields.description: The current status of the run.

fields.name: Task
fields.description: The task against which run was scheduled.

fields.name: TimerTrigger
fields.description: The timer trigger that caused the run.

fields.name: UpdateTriggerToken
fields.description: The update trigger token passed for the Run.
